{{Infobox company | name = KidzDunya | logo =[[File:KidzDunya Logo 2014 PNG file Low Resolution.png|right]] | caption = KidzDunya Corporate Logo | type = [[Family Entertainment Center]] | genre = <!-- Only used with media and publishing companies --> | fate = | predecessor = | successor = | foundation = <!-- {{Start date|2012|MM|DD}} --> | founder = | defunct = <!-- {{End date|YYYY|MM|DD}} --> | location_city = [[Karachi]] | location_country = [[Pakistan]] | location = Dolmen Mall Clifton | locations = | area_served = | key_people = | industry = Entertainment | products = | services = | revenue = | operating_income = | net_income = | aum = <!-- Only used with financial services companies --> | assets = | equity = | owner = | num_employees = | parent = | divisions = | subsid = | traded_as = | homepage = [http://www.KidzDunya.com KidzDunya.com] | footnotes = | intl = }} '''KidzDunya''' is a privately held Pakistani company. Currently operating in Karachi, Pakistan. They have only one branch in all of Pakistan, which is in Clifton, Karachi. They are based on the popular theme park called [[KidZania]] that holds multiple branches around the world.
==Overview== KidzDunya is themed as a child-sized replica of a real city, including buildings, shops and restaurants, as well as vehicles moving along its streets. In this city, children aged 4 through 14, work in branded activities and run the world.<ref>{{cite news|title='KidzDunya’ teaches your 5-year-old to get a job and manage money!|url=http://blogs.tribune.com.pk/story/19931/kidz-dunya-teaches-your-5-year-old-to-get-a-job-and-manage-money/|accessdate=8 July 2014|publisher=Tribune|ref=1}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=KidzDunya - Its a Kids World Baby |url=http://oyekarachi.com/kidzdunya-its-a-kids-world-baby/ |website=Oye Pakistan |accessdate=8 July 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714150726/http://oyekarachi.com/kidzdunya-its-a-kids-world-baby/ |archivedate=14 July 2014 |df= }}</ref>
